WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.006 --> 00:00:07.507
[sinister music playing]

2
00:00:11.511 --> 00:00:14.139
[Becky groans. winces]

3
00:00:14.806 --> 00:00:17.308
[Ángela] I'm sorry
about the inconvenience.

4
00:00:17.392 --> 00:00:20.311
Electrical current is dangerous.

5
00:00:20.395 --> 00:00:21.730
Just like you.

6
00:00:21.813 --> 00:00:22.981
[Becky gasps]

7
00:00:23.064 --> 00:00:23.898
[Oliver] Ángela?

8
00:00:23.982 --> 00:00:27.569
- Oliver. you're just in time for the show.
- What's going on here?

9
00:00:27.652 --> 00:00:30.030
- No. no. no. This is a bad idea.
- Hey. hey. hey!

10
00:00:30.113 --> 00:00:32.407
Help me finish this bitch.
or get the hell out of here.

11
00:00:33.158 --> 00:00:35.368
[Oliver] She made a mistake.
but you can't kill her.

12
00:00:35.452 --> 00:00:36.953
She screwed up twice.

13
00:00:37.037 --> 00:00:39.456
Those dancers should be dead by now.

14
00:00:39.539 --> 00:00:43.168
beginning with that piece of trash.
Ms. Jade Monroe.

15
00:00:44.169 --> 00:00:45.837
So why can't I kill her?

16
00:00:46.629 --> 00:00:47.630
Okay.

17
00:00:48.548 --> 00:00:49.382
Murder her.

18
00:00:50.258 --> 00:00:52.719
But be prepared to lose your son forever.

19
00:00:53.470 --> 00:00:56.306
Because Lucas will never forgive you.

20
00:00:57.515 --> 00:00:58.433
Ever.

21
00:00:58.516 --> 00:01:00.602
[suspenseful music playing]

22
00:01:08.860 --> 00:01:10.195
[Norris] We were just talking.

23
00:01:10.278 --> 00:01:13.364
I heard the alarm beep.
and then boom. the car exploded.

24
00:01:13.448 --> 00:01:15.950
[Indira] Right when I turned off
the alarm. it exploded.

25
00:01:16.534 --> 00:01:18.578
We have to consult with the experts now.

26
00:01:19.496 --> 00:01:20.914
Need to go to the hospital?

27
00:01:20.997 --> 00:01:21.831
- No.
- Me neither.

28
00:01:22.499 --> 00:01:26.002
Sir. the explosives were wired
into the car's electrical system.

29
00:01:27.212 --> 00:01:28.213
Excuse me.

30
00:01:29.631 --> 00:01:31.299
[suspenseful music playing]

31
00:01:35.678 --> 00:01:36.846
[music ends]

32
00:01:36.930 --> 00:01:38.348
[theme music playing]

33
00:01:39.432 --> 00:01:41.643
FAKE PROFILE

34
00:01:41.726 --> 00:01:43.895
