35
00:01:44.896 --> 00:01:48.316
{\an8}<i>♪ Keep going when the wheels fall off ♪</i>

36
00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:50.068
{\an8}TWO WEEKS LATER

37
00:01:50.151 --> 00:01:55.281
{\an8}<i>♪ Pick up your broken dreams</i>
<i>And dust them off ♪</i>

38
00:01:55.782 --> 00:01:59.202
<i>♪ It's time to let the needle drop ♪</i>

39
00:01:59.285 --> 00:02:00.370
[Miguel] Hey. champ.

40
00:02:03.039 --> 00:02:04.332
I brought you a gift.

41
00:02:09.420 --> 00:02:10.797
Can I ask you a question?

42
00:02:10.880 --> 00:02:13.133
What do you gain by treating me like this?

43
00:02:13.216 --> 00:02:16.761
By holding on to anger.
to your resentment and hatred?

44
00:02:17.387 --> 00:02:18.221
Answer me.

45
00:02:18.304 --> 00:02:20.265
Lucas. why do you hate me?

46
00:02:20.348 --> 00:02:22.559
- I don't hate you.
- What then?

47
00:02:22.642 --> 00:02:24.185
I just want you to disappear.

48
00:02:24.269 --> 00:02:25.895
so I never have to look
at your face again.

49
00:02:25.979 --> 00:02:29.357
Well. that's not happening. Lucas.
You're my son. and I'm your father.

50
00:02:29.440 --> 00:02:31.067
I intend to stick around.

51
00:02:31.151 --> 00:02:34.112
We used to have
a great father-son relationship.

52
00:02:34.195 --> 00:02:37.031
Until you broke Mom's heart
with all your pathetic affairs.

53
00:02:37.115 --> 00:02:39.576
and I don't regret telling Camila
about you and Becky.

54
00:02:39.659 --> 00:02:42.537
I feel sorry for her.
She doesn't know what a monster you are.

55
00:02:42.620 --> 00:02:45.707
[Ángela] Miguel. what a surprise.
What brings you to my house?

56
00:02:45.790 --> 00:02:48.376
[Miguel] I just came by to visit Lucas.
That's all.

57
00:02:51.296 --> 00:02:53.506
Lucas. you know where Eva is?

58
00:02:53.590 --> 00:02:55.300
Where she always is. at Camila's.

59
00:02:55.383 --> 00:02:59.971
[dramatic sting]

60
00:03:04.184 --> 00:03:06.436
- Did I show you my dress?
- [Camila] No. not yet.

61
00:03:06.519 --> 00:03:08.271
- Oh. I have to! It's beautiful…
- Let me see.

62
00:03:08.354 --> 00:03:09.731
Show me the photo.

63
00:03:09.814 --> 00:03:11.024
It's amazing.

64
00:03:11.107 --> 00:03:13.526
- I love it. Cami. but I'm so nervous.
- Ooh.

65
00:03:13.610 --> 00:03:15.862
- Why?
- I don't know. I just am.

66
00:03:15.945 --> 00:03:18.656
Sorry for interrupting.
but the door was open.

67
00:03:19.407 --> 00:03:20.825
Good afternoon. Camila.

68
00:03:20.909 --> 00:03:22.076
How are you. Ángela?

69
00:03:22.827 --> 00:03:24.913
Very well. thanks. Hi. Eva.

70
00:03:24.996 --> 00:03:26.372
What happened?

71
00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:30.376
Well. sweetie. look.

72
00:03:31.294 --> 00:03:34.130
Camila and your father aren't
together anymore.

73
00:03:34.214 --> 00:03:36.674
so it's not a good idea to come here.

74
00:03:36.758 --> 00:03:39.135
- [Eva] Mmm.
- Don't worry. Ángela. It's not a problem.

75
00:03:39.219 --> 00:03:42.222
Well. Camila. you know Eva adores you.

76
00:03:43.598 --> 00:03:46.351
Will you go back to our house? Yes?

77
00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:49.562
I love you so much. Cami.

78
00:03:49.646 --> 00:03:50.480
Bye.

79
00:03:50.563 --> 00:03:51.648
[tense music playing]

80
00:03:51.731 --> 00:03:53.483
You owe me a photo
of you in the dress. right?

81
00:03:53.566 --> 00:03:55.526
- I'll send you one.
- Can't wait to see it.

82
00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:03.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
