<i>♪ Can't help when I look at you ♪</i>

585
00:31:54.913 --> 00:31:57.040
<i>♪ Dramatic ♪</i>

586
00:31:57.123 --> 00:31:59.208
<i>♪ I panic ♪</i>

587
