588
00:32:20.605 --> 00:32:23.191
<i>♪ Losing control ♪</i>

589
00:32:24.859 --> 00:32:29.113
<i>♪ Can't let it go. go. go. go. go. go ♪</i>

590
00:32:31.616 --> 00:32:36.204
<i>♪ Is this heaven or is this hell? ♪</i>

591
